This project is still in development, and may contain bugs.
Achoo aims to produce a fast installation of basic Arch Linux with Xfce desktop
environment and LXDM greeter.

How to use it:

1) You should be running a live Arch session (as 'root') with a working internet connection

2) First update the package list and install git: pacman -Sy git

3) Next get the script from Github: git clone git://github.com/Angeltoast/Achoo

4) Then run it: cd Achoo && ./achoo
